eType) => boolean>;\n   const canSwitch = listeners.length === 0 || listeners.ev
ery(fn => fn(sceneType));\n   ```\n   This changes from `this.emit(\'before-swit
ch\', sceneType)` (which returns true if no listeners) to checking all listeners
return true. This is a bug fix since emit\'s return value doesn\'t work the way 
the old code expected. Good.\n\n9. **Tests don\'t actually run** - `vitest: comm
and not found` because node_modules is missing. This is an environment issue, no
t a code issue.\n\n10. **Documentation updates**:\n    - `docs/design-docs/ui-st
yle-guide/03-component.md` updated (warning color changed from goldBrown to warn
ing)\n    - `docs/modules/client/ui.md` updated\n    - But PRD-004 says `docs/fr
ontend/ui-components.md` should be rewritten. Looking at `.doc-coverage.txt`, th
e PR changes `docs/design-docs/ui-style-guide/03-component.md` and `docs/modules
/client/ui.md`. The `docs/frontend/ui-components.md` is not in the changed files
list. But AGENTS.md says "本 PRD 替代旧版 PRD" for `docs/frontend/ui-components.
