` 已重写为本 PRD 内容. But the PR doesn\'t touch that file. This is a documentat
ion gap.\n\n11. **UITheme.warning inconsistency in design spec**:\n    `designs/
issue-19/design-spec.md` section 3.3 and 3.4 specify `UITheme.goldBrown` for war
ning, but the actual code uses `UITheme.warning` (0xffaa00). The `docs/design-do
cs/ui-style-guide/03-component.md` was updated to use `UITheme.warning`. So the 
design spec document is inconsistent with the actual implementation and the upda
ted style guide. This is a documentation bug in the design artifact.\n\n12. **Pr
ogressToast.ts uses ToastManager.getInstance(scene)** but passes no `startY`. Th
e old code did `new ToastManager(scene, startY)`. The new `getInstance` doesn\'t
